{"tid":1688623,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"人權法仲有嘢可以做！搵21個聯署咗新疆人權法嘅議員聯署埋香港人權法","createTime":"2019-11-02T13:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T16:21:32.000Z","uid":81879,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc24f5a95f358d192c1d53ffcacc4e2b9cf19e9","tid":1688623,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kongstate/status/1190497266680942592?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkongstate%2Fstatus%2F1190497266680942592%3Fs%3D21&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=ed7af54f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkongstate%2Fstatus%2F1190497266680942592%3Fs%3D21&h=899b8f0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kongstate/status/1190497266680942592?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n原來有成21個未聯署香港人權法！我地而家仲爭24個就夠60, 足夠抵抗被嗰幾個議員拖！"},{"pid":"5ac25d85b471a5598dd005467eff0b82991bcff0","tid":1688623,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:29:33.000Z","msg":"未輸㗎！"},{"pid":"7967189f8c88ab32f2ab65f74b8f42687afe6ce1","tid":1688623,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"102f62ea4eb31ecfd68025027e86f67f68d3e710","tid":1688623,"uid":106601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:32:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ec7741cf0749e3d155ad3c0348b387f1494ef1c","tid":1688623,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:40:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbd7862a39079e482089899156ffacd407d90ba","tid":1688623,"uid":111576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"71a0eafc042fce822fd27f235bcc81d8a73c7b0b","tid":1688623,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:44:43.000Z","msg":"幫手retweet!"},{"pid":"a2823c7ddd5de3b5a1597292a3f487a459767964","tid":1688623,"uid":225798,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:47:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/142135802497882/posts/2762847053760064/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F142135802497882%2Fposts%2F2762847053760064%2F&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=06ca9db3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/142135802497882/posts/2762847053760064/</a><br />\n<br />\nSolomon Yue雖然被熱普城班友搞，但佢嘅Twitter仍然係十分之有益，例如 香港人權及民主法 ，當啲大淡友(好多包括大中華膠)係咁唱淡果陣，Solomon Yue提大家，要攞多24張co-sponsor令到啲反對者收聲，儘量將法案通過，而24張飛邊度嚟嘅呢，大家就要學數飛。<br />\n<br />\n香港人權及民主法 學數飛<br />\n英國政黨黨鞭本來嘅作用，係負責寫信俾各大議員，督促佢哋投票，所以黨鞭最基本責任係數飛，數咗飛，至知下一步啲票點拉。由大學學生會，到出嚟選校友會，都係要學數飛，更何況現實政治。而 Solomon Yue 提36個co-sponsor，名單列晒喺度。<br />\n<br />\n容我咁講，2019年10月31日仍然有議員簽咗co-sponsor，即係有議員肯做，大家唔好灰心，有啲大淡友真係居心有啲問題。問題果24條友邊度搵，其實我咁睇：<br />\n<br />\n上面個表有列有份co-sponsor嘅州份，因為senate不論州份大小，每州2席，所以已經爆咗果啲，你唔駛再挖。<br />\n依家係民主黨18張，共和黨17張，獨立1張，民主黨主導嘅眾議院既然過咗個法案，而民主黨有45張飛，即係有27張可以挖，所以應該有一路人馬，係挖盡民主黨嘅飛，攞咗十張，係你已經好舒服，如Solomon Yue，有80人支持，咁民主黨搵多12個都唔過份。<br />\n左膠至愛嘅Bernie Sanders，依家未co-sponsor，點解無左膠要佢co-sponsor嘅，有一張就一張喇。如果佢都唔co-sponsor，我真係好懷疑左膠愛佢啲乜，隨時佢只不過係一個偽君子。<br />\n共和黨要再挖，其實都得，最好表過態支持香港果啲，多謝一吓佢，然後提佢co-sponsor。如果共和民主黨同步挖，係有機會呢個月中之前，就攞夠co-sponsor嘅飛，制止拉布，或其他荒謬嘅反對，亦迫Mitch McConnell做嘢，以最優先次序搞掂佢。<br />\n做任何形式政治游說都要數一數飛，然後節省時間做嘢，與其做果啲膠到爆嘅白宮聯署，點解唔喺Senate拉票度做實事，所以我成日話熱狗班冚家富貴係浪費大家時間，亦係呢個原因。<br />\n<br />\n當然，有心人請列出未co-sponsor，但唔似會反對果啲人嘅清單，我都會整理一吓，然後再同大家分享。但Solomon Yue真係熟書，稍作提點其實已經提供好清楚嘅方向，美國政治有啲遊戲規則，係比英國清楚，英國有時朝野嘅走向都要估估吓，但美國係可以唔駛點估，因為好多資訊都攤喺眼光之下，熱狗、大中華膠要誤導大家，恐怕無咁容易。"},{"pid":"c0fbcdb9a77ff03fb99d22a36307bb4ba434df6e","tid":1688623,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:49:18.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入 /task3</span></span><br />\n燒背 候選人被捕 消防員被警察毆打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e6a8a435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"88ca2ad8de05536e2bce10c95c02b63ec94a3c71","tid":1688623,"uid":46299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099339aa00b3330abb96633fa3c8a705d7962009","tid":1688623,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c7bfe23ea0e96f0042d6e7ec076e40fa49ad38b","tid":1688623,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"3790eb4a5ab69f8876d1da668570cdd32f1cd16a","tid":1688623,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:24:56.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"97d5125d8239259fb504795cd361779963da0465","tid":1688623,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:01:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a26a9d0f39a0ef0a879ee7fab6245b50efd0765","tid":1688623,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1dzZ3EauDW_Biju2QzacPKs29lLovWTMLSjE1zKncZ8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1dzZ3EauDW_Biju2QzacPKs29lLovWTMLSjE1zKncZ8Q&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=1f9b831c\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1dzZ3EauDW_Biju2QzacPKs29lLovWTMLSjE1zKncZ8Q</a><br />\n<br />\n整咗個workbook裝住參議員嘅twitter"},{"pid":"423b4d83360e78348c748afdc11dfa60382d4d81","tid":1